quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  19,39,"“Ndipo achenjeze (anthu) za tsiku la madandaulo, pamene chiweruzo chidzagamulidwa, (abwino kulowa ku munda wamtendere, oipa kulowa ku Moto); koma iwo (pano pa dziko lapansi) ali m’kusalabadira ndipo sakhulupirira"
  19,40,“Ndithu Ife Tidzaitenga nthaka ndi amene ali pamenepo; (zonse zidzakhala za Ife) ndipo kwa Ife adzabwerera
  19,41,"“Ndipo mtchule m’buku ili, Ibrahim. Ndithu iye adali wonena zoona zokhazokha, Mneneri"
  19,42,"“(Akumbutse) pamene iye adauza bambo wake: “E inu bambo wanga! Bwanji mukupembedza zomwe sizimva ndiponso sizipenya, ndiponso Zosakupindulitsani chilichonse?”"
  19,43,““E inu bambo wanga! Ndithu ine zandidzera nzeru (zomuzindikira Allah) zomwe sizidakudzereni; choncho nditsateni. Ndikutsogolereni ku njira yolungama.”
  19,44,““E bambo wanga! Musapembedze satana (potsatira malangizo ake). Ndithu satana ngopandukira (Allah) Mwini chifundo chambiri.”
  19,45,"“E bambo wanga! Ndithu ine ndikuopa kuti chilango chingakukhudzeni chochokera kwa (Allah) Mwini chifundo chambiri, ndipo potero mdzakhala bwenzi la satana.”"
  19,46,"“(Bambo wake) adati: “Kodi iwe ukuda milungu yanga, E iwe Ibrahim? Ngati susiya (kunyoza milungu yanga) ndikugenda ndi miyala; choncho ndichokere kwa nthawi yaitali (tisaonanenso).”"
  19,47,"“(Ibrahim) adati: “Mtendere ukhale pa inu! Ndikupempherani chikhululuko kwa Mbuye wanga (ngakhale mwandipirikitsa). Ndithu iye amandichitira chisoni kwambiri.”"
  19,48,““Ndipo ine ndikupatukirani ku zomwe mukuzipembedzazo kusiya Allah ndipo ndipempha Mbuye wanga; ndithu sindikhala watsoka popempha Mbuye wanga.”
  19,49,"“Ndipo pamene adawapatukira ndi zimene adali kuzipembedza kusiya Allah, tidampatsa iye Ishaq, ndi Ya’qub, ndipo aliyense wa iwo tidampanga kukhala m’neneri"
  19,50,"“Ndipo tidawapatsa iwo chifundo Chathu, ndi kuwayikira iwo kutchulidwa kwabwino, kwapamwamba (pakati pa zolengedwa)"
  19,51,"“Ndipo mtchule Mûsa m’buku (ili). Ndithu iye adali wosankhidwa ndi woyeretsedwa: ndipo adali Mtumiki M’neneri"